{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on a thrilling turn-based strategy pirate game that masterfully blends roguelike elements with intense arena naval combat. Make critical decisions, adapt to ever-changing situations, and outsmart your enemies at every turn. Command your ship through fierce battles and rise as the ultimate pirate champion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/Header_1.png?t=1732106646\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/1.gif?t=1732106646\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Execute moves simultaneously for strategic prediction and positioning.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Navigate obstacles and leverage the environment to your advantage.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Utilize the wind to reduce movement costs when sailing with it, avoid the storm or use it to escape chasing players.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Fear the ever-growing curse of the sea.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/Header_2.png?t=1732106646\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/2.gif?t=1732106646\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Pick between various upgrades to increase your power.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Unleash environmental chaos causing misfortune throughout the seven seas, giving you both advantages and disadvantages.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Steer the course of battle by picking between special mythic perks with even greater powers.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/Header_3.png?t=1732106646\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/3.gif?t=1732106646\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Manage your crew, giving them tasks like fishing, treasure hunting, and resource gathering.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Upgrade your ship and customize components for increased sail speed, greater defenses, better vision, and faster repairs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Pick and play a role in your fleet and contribute to a strongly drafted crew.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/Header_4.png?t=1732106646\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/4.gif?t=1732106646\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Challenge epic bosses, wield their powers, and unlock abilities to cause havoc.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Fight sea monsters for valuable upgrades and significant buffs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Defeat AI fleets and mighty pirate ships, or invite them to battle on your side for a good deal.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/Header_5.png?t=1732106646\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/5.gif?t=1732106646\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Participate in game modes like free-for-all, co-op, and team battles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Climb the ELO ranks by matching against skill-level opponents.<br><br></p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732106646","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/page.bg.jpg?t=1732106646","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3